set style line 3 lc rgb '#2e8b57' pt 3 ps 1 lt 3 lw 2 # --- green
set style line 4 lc rgb '#0060ad' pt 4 ps 1 lt 4 lw 2 # --- blue
set style line 5 lc rgb '#ff8c00' pt 5 ps 1 lt 5 lw 2 # --- orange
